msgstr "莫洛克人"

#: .\NPC\classes.json
msgid "I live in the sewer now.  That about sums it up."
msgstr "我现在住下水道了。差不多就这样。"

#: .\NPC\classes.json
msgid "morlock trader"
msgstr "摩洛克商人"

#: .\NPC\classes.json
msgid "I make trade deals for the morlocks."
msgstr "我为摩洛克人处理贸易事务。"

#: .\NPC\classes.json
